---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="min-h-screen w-full flex items-center">
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-12 pt-36 pb-16">

    <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col gap-6">
      <p class="text-pink-500 text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase">
        Comunidad Deportiva CDMX
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-tight">
        Discipline will take you places motivation can't
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-md">
        Encuentra eventos deportivos en la Ciudad de México, únete a grupos, comparte tus rutas y conecta con personas que comparten tu pasión.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-2 w-fit relative group cursor-pointer">
        <img
          src={base + "boton-1.svg"}
          alt="Únete"
          class="h-14 w-auto object-contain block group-hover:opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-200"
        />
        <img
          src={base + "boton-2.svg"}
          alt="Únete"
          class="h-14 w-auto object-contain absolute inset-0 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-200"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex-1 flex items-center justify-center">
      <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg aspect-video rounded-3xl overflow-hidden
                  bg-white/10
                  backdrop-blur-md
                  border border-white/20
                  shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(255,45,120,0.2)]
                  transform rotate-3 hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-700">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1/3 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/20 to-transparent z-10"></div>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center text-white/20 text-sm">
          1400 × 900px
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>